** XML building command

  Full options are :
  
   <<-d>> (debug)     : debug activation
   
   <<-f>> (force)     : force XML compile even if MDB is up to date
   
   <<-g>> (game) GAME : game short name like : mtg
   
   <<-h>> (help)      : print this help message and exit
   
   <<-n>> (nopaymana) : ignore all 'paya-mana' actions
   
   <<-v>> (version)   : print product version and exit
   
   <<-x>> (xsd)       : enable XSD validation
   